<div class='mt-4' data-controller='tag-score-chart'
     data-tag-score-chart-summary-value='<%= json_escape(tag_score_summary.to_json) %>'>
    <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-2 border-b border-gray-200'>
        <% tag_score_summary.each do |section_key, section| %>
            <button type='button' class='border-b-2 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold'
                    data-tag-score-chart-target='tab' data-section-key='<%= section_key %>'
                    data-action='tag-score-chart#select'>
                <%= section[:label] %>
            </button>
        <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class='mt-4 rounded border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-gray-700'>
        <p data-tag-score-chart-target='note'></p>
        <p>複数の分野にまたがる問題は、それぞれの分野に加算されます。</p>
    </div>

    <div class='mt-6 h-96 md:h-[30rem]'>
        <canvas data-tag-score-chart-target='canvas'></canvas>
        <p class='hidden py-10 text-center text-gray-500' data-tag-score-chart-target='empty'>
            表示できるタグ別集計がありません。
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
